




{"id":8623,"date":"2021-09-29T15:03:09","date_gmt":"2021-09-29T08:03:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=8623"},"modified":"2022-05-19T16:55:16","modified_gmt":"2022-05-19T09:55:16","slug":"su-khac-nhau-giua-camera-va-webcam-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-nhau-giua-camera-va-webcam-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c nhau gi\u1eefa camera v\u00e0 webcam l\u00e0 g\u00ec?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-nhau-giua-camera-va-webcam-la-gi\/#webcam_la_gi_co_nen_lua_chon_webcam_cho_hop_truc_tuyen\" >Webcam l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f3 n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn webcam cho h\u1ecdp tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-nhau-giua-camera-va-webcam-la-gi\/#camera_hoi_nghi_la_gi_co_gi_khac_so_voi_webcam\" >Camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi webcam?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/su-khac-nhau-giua-camera-va-webcam-la-gi\/#su_dung_camera_va_webcam_theo_muc_dich\" >S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera v\u00e0 webcam theo m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u1ecbch Covid di\u1ec5n ra c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf kinh doanh, c\u00f4ng ty ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0. V\u00ec v\u1eady, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn nh\u1edd c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i internet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n, chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi nhau nh\u1edd camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 webcam. Hai thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c nhau, t\u00f9y v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. V\u1eady s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa camera v\u00e0 webcam nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o? L\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p chi ti\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u00f3 trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"webcam_la_gi_co_nen_lua_chon_webcam_cho_hop_truc_tuyen\"><\/span><b>Webcam l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f3 n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn webcam cho h\u1ecdp tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">Webcam l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng camera chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdp c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n,&#8230;Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u1ecdp tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n, trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n b\u00e8, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8627 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/Anh-chup-Man-hinh-2021-09-29-luc-14.56.07.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"779\" height=\"498\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">Webcam c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c tr\u00ean k\u1ec7 tivi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi. N\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn webcam thay v\u00ec h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng camera tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, laptop th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd, webcam cho ra ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh t\u1ed1t, s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e2m thanh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 webcam tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00ednh n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea5y n\u00e9t v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nhi\u1ec5u, t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng,&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"camera_hoi_nghi_la_gi_co_gi_khac_so_voi_webcam\"><\/span><b><span lang=\"vi\">Camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi webcam?<\/span><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">Camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb ghi h\u00ecnh k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1eeb 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1ea5t k\u00ec, gi\u00fap truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c qua m\u1ea1ng internet. Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">\u0110i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb v\u00e0 webcam d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng cho c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp v\u1eeba v\u00e0 l\u1edbn, s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia tr\u00ean 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, tuy l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng camera c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0ng do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p t\u00ednh n\u0103ng quay Pan-Tilt-Zoom n\u00ean cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quay v\u1edbi g\u00f3c r\u1ed9ng. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu ph\u00f3ng g\u1ea5p m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8625 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/VC220.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"523\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">Nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edch h\u1ee3p all-in-one c\u1ea3 microphone v\u00e0 loa ngo\u00e0i. V\u00ec v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong ph\u00f2ng h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb r\u1ed9ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 sau: 1 camera c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u00e1c d\u00e0n loa v\u00e0 mic theo h\u00ecnh chu\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u00e2m thanh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0: \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i full HD 4K, t\u1ef1 x\u1eed l\u00fd nhi\u1ec5u v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaft \u00e2m thanh t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb xa,&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8626 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/su-dung-camera-hoi-nghi-truc-tuyen.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su_dung_camera_va_webcam_theo_muc_dich\"><\/span><b>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera v\u00e0 webcam theo m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, tuy m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a webcam kh\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u00e0 \u00e2m thanh nh\u01b0 camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ph\u00ed. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta r\u00fat ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng webcam cho ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp nh\u00f3m \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb, h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp l\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8624\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/videoconference.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><span lang=\"vi\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c nhau gi\u1eefa camera v\u00e0 webcam ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb h\u1ecdp tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u1ecbch Covid di\u1ec5n ra c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf kinh doanh, c\u00f4ng ty ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0. V\u00ec v\u1eady, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn nh\u1edd c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i internet \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9108,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8623","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail",